Spellcaster "Cerulean" monster in your Monster Zone cannot be targeted by your opponents card effects. If this face-up card leaves the field: Destroy all monsters you control that were Special Summoned from the Extra Deck. You can only use the following effect of "Cerulean Legacy" once per turn. You can activate 1 of these effects;
● Special Summon 1 "Cerulean Magus" from your hand or GY.
● You can add 1 "Shining Azure Flash" or 1 "Cerulean Siren Cry" from your Deck to your hand.
